{"title":"红雨","authors":["严阵"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":3,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红雨（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严阵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二月的雨：红雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无声地，洒遍了江南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗雨点染红一个骨朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗雨点染红一张笑脸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村外的水声：拍拍，拍拍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村庄上罩着淡烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子们赤着脚跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰起头，笑着去迎雨点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻人，围拢在公社门前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抚摸着新铸的犁尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争着去开第一犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓑衣都不穿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有拖拉机手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把机子试了一遍又一遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着不停的雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在窗前不停地转圈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗雨点染红一个骨朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗雨点染红一张笑脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二月的雨：红雨呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无声地，染红了江南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江堤新柳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江堤上长起一排新柳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫩绿的叶芽比花还香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把锹插在肥堆旁边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花棉袄搭在柳树枝上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁挑着沉重的担子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞过石桥，一步一晃？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶牛的老汉直起腰看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗衣的大妈眯着眼望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村头上不知是谁在笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑声儿低，话声儿高："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这是我们的新队长哎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就是投了她的票……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知是哪个调皮鬼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"存心想开一个玩笑："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄躲在石桥下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学那布谷鸟叫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咕咕，一声，咕咕，一声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把女队长吓了一跳："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她放下担儿望天边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心想：莫非我们晚了？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}